'''魯本·平托'''（{{lang-pt|Rúben Pinto}}；{{bd|1992年|4月24日}}）是一位[[葡萄牙|葡萄牙]]足球運動員。在場上的位置是中場。他現在效力於[[索菲亚中央陆军|索菲亚中央陆军]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.fcpf.pt/noticias-ruben-pinto-assina-pelo-fc-pacos-de-ferreira |title=Rúben Pinto assina pelo FC Paços de Ferreira |language=pt |trans_title=Rúben Pinto signs for FC Paços de Ferreira |date=7 January 2015 |website=[[F.C._Paços_de_Ferreira|F.C. Paços de Ferreira]] |accessdate=8 January 2015 |archive-date=2016-04-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160401125218/http://www.fcpf.pt/noticias-ruben-pinto-assina-pelo-fc-pacos-de-ferreira |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他也代表葡萄牙U21國家足球隊參賽<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.record.xl.pt/Futebol/selecoes/sub21//interior.aspx?content_id=825197|title=Portugal-Croácia, 2–0|trans_title=Portugal-Croatia, 2–0|publisher=Record|language=pt|date=2 June 2013|accessdate=10 June 2013|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130607113619/http://www.record.xl.pt/Futebol/selecoes/sub21/interior.aspx?content_id=825197|archivedate=2013年6月7日}}</ref>。

